            whatDistinguishesThisLevel: "Analyze requires the student to work from data or a scenario to a conclusion. 'A cell accumulates fructose-6-phosphate and depletes fructose-1,6-bisphosphate — identify which enzyme is most likely inhibited and explain why.' The student must determine the answer from the pattern, not recall it.",
